---
// Compressed, type-only hero (~55vh). Copy is server-rendered; the `reveal` class
// only adds a JS scroll-in fade (no-JS / reduced-motion show it immediately).
---

<section class="build-hero">
  <div class="reveal shell build-hero__inner">
    <h1 class="build-hero__title">
      Five shapes of <span class="build-hero__italic">bespoke software</span>.
    </h1>
    <p class="build-hero__sub">
      Software is the product. The shape it takes depends on what your
      operation actually needs.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
